room_title: Escape room "Narcos" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
review: My family and I just went twice; first was split room and second was Veronica. Both times were very fun. We love how we were submerses in the atmosphere and the challenging riddles and puzzles. Will definitely do it again.

review: Creepy...I loved how the game tied into SPLIT (another one of their rooms).  Staff is great! Thanks Panic!
